          {
            "commit": "c3e985e7e98f41ebf5ecb78887dcd2554601f7ef",
            "subject": "LU-56 ptlrpc: post rqbd with flag LNET_INS_LOCAL"
          }
        ],
        "author": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-07-08 16:11:08.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-07-08 16:11:08.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-181 ptlrpc: align fields of ptlrpc_request",
        "message": "LU-181 ptlrpc: align fields of ptlrpc_request\n\nSize of ptlrpc_request_buffer_desc is 1048 which means we need 2K\nslab for allocating rqbd. This can be changed after we align\nfields in ptlrpc_reques to decrease size of ptlrpc_requestt,\nbecause each rqbd has an embedded ptlrpc_request.\nWe also aligned fields of lu_context because it's embedded in\nptlrpc_request.\n\nWith this simple change, size of rqbd is 1008 bytes, and we\ncan save at least tens of MBs on server.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Iac292e4375421843785fdae083b1aa667d43b3a7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
